items.title: Niva Bupa Health Insurance IPO: Should investors subscribe?
items.description: Low penetration of health insurance, high out-of-pocket expenses, consistently higher healthcare inflation, and increased awareness are some of the structural factors that will drive the demand for retail healthcare insurance

items.title: Abbott India posts 15% rise in Q2 profit on strong demand, price hikes
items.description: Abbott India continued to benefit from anti-infectives and medications for gastrointestinal conditions, the company said
